To build the codec 
1) grab newest version of library from http://adplug.sourceforge.net/
2) apply xbmc.diff
3) go into the top source directory
4) run:
     aclocal -I .
     libtoolize --automake --copy --force
     automake --add-missing --copy --force
     autoconf --force
5) go back to the parent directory
6) run 'make'
7) you will now have your library as adplug-$(ARCH).so

current svn is based on v2.1
